==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Undecreed
<hw>Un`de*creed"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<ety>[Pref. <ets>un-</ets> not + <ets>decreed</ets>.]</ety> <def>Not
decreed.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <ety>[1st pref. <ets>un-</ets> +
<ets>decree</ets>.]</ety> <def>Reversed or nullified by decree, as
something previously decreed.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Undecyl</ent>⟦br⟧
